PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Joel Eusevio DAVIS, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 156406
COA: 332081 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 11, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellee to extend the time for filing his brief is GRANTED. The brief submitted on October 5, 2018, is accepted as timely filed.
